&lt;li&gt;Build a strong field/product feedback loop by analysing qualitative and quantitative data and regularly shadowing Sales and Customer Success calls.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally: partner with stakeholders across the business on key strategic and operational priorities for our Security business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
